metadata.name: T-shirt | Spring 22
metadata.description:
Fashion Weak is a digital fashion collection reappropriating known pieces and codes of fashion while denouncing questionable practices of the industry. The collection is composed of 13 pieces representing the number of weeks in the season.

The Spring 22 Collection is made up of aesthetic pieces that highlight animal suffering by using a part of the animal that is neglected in favor of leather and fur: the bones.

100% digital bones
